      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Clean title. Garage kept. Inspection reports available.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    }
  ],
